---
title: North Indian Tofu Curry  with fragrant garlic rice
description: This aromatic veggie curry is a tapestry of tastes and textures. Crispy tofu, charred mushrooms, zippy chives and fragrant garlic rice are only a few of the elements that make this dish delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W19_IE_IEVCLV15145-3_Main_high-f45937f6.jpg
